profile: PLG Builders strives for excellence in every building project we do. Our detail-oriented team of licensed and insured contractors listens to you. We do whatever we can to make your dreams a reality when it comes to deck construction, fence construction, repairs, renovation, remodelling, carpentry, and new construction. We work with the top developers in New Brunswick and are the local Home Depot Pro you can trust for professionalism and quality craftsmanship.
services: Construction, Framing, Deck Building, Fence Building, Home Builder, Home Remodel, Demolition, Concrete removal, building demolition, Mini Excavator services
payment_method: Cash, Cheque, Visa, Mastercard, American Express, E-Transfer
